OL,3,CFlash flooding in Somerset after
OL,4,Ccounty hit by 18,540 lightning strikes
OL,6,FWatch the flooding develop in
OL,7,FGlastonbury over the course of 20
OL,8,Fminutes. Video credit: Michelle
OL,9,FCowbourne.
OL,11,FHomes and businesses in Somerset are
OL,12,Fdealing with the aftermath of flash
OL,13,Fflooding, after the county was the
OL,14,Fworst hit in the country by the
OL,15,Fextreme weather.
OL,17,FThe Met Office said 29,074 lightning
OL,18,Fstrikes were recorded in the UK in the
OL,19,Flast 24 hours to 9am on Tuesday 23
OL,20,FJune, with the majority ` 18,540 `
OL,21,Fover Somerset.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/5
