OL,3,CFlash flooding in Somerset after
OL,4,Ccounty hit by 18,540 lightning strikes
OL,6,FFlash floods were reported across the
OL,7,Fcounty, including in Glastonbury.
OL,9,FMichelle Cowbourne owns the Vision of
OL,10,FSomerset shop on the Market Place and
OL,11,Flost some of her stock after
OL,12,Ffloodwater built up on the street.
OL,14,F"Community spirit was great with
OL,15,Feveryone helping each other," she said.
OL,17,FAnother video shows the rainwater
OL,18,Fpouring down the street. Credit: Linda
OL,19,FRavenscroft.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/5
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
