PN,40903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F409A1782402489
OL,3,CFlash flooding in Somerset after
OL,4,Ccounty hit by 18,540 lightning strikes
OL,6,FThe Mystic Garden Gallery on the
OL,7,FMarket Place also dealt with some
OL,8,Fleaks, with owner Linda Ravenscroft
OL,9,Fsharing footage of bins floating down
OL,10,Fthe road.
OL,12,FShe described the weather as
OL,13,F"biblical" and said she had been
OL,14,F"luckier than some".
OL,16,FMeanwhile, in Bath, the central
OL,17,Flibrary has experienced "extensive
OL,18,Fleaks" after the storm and has been
OL,19,Fforced to close.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/5
