OL,3,CFlash flooding in Somerset after
OL,4,Ccounty hit by 18,540 lightning strikes
OL,6,FBath and North East Somerset Council
OL,7,Fsaid: "Following an hour of intense
OL,8,Fthunderstorm and heavy rain we are
OL,9,Fdealing with a number of incidents and
OL,10,Fflash floods on our roads.
OL,12,F"Thank you to residents for reporting
OL,13,Fissues. Please bear with us while we
OL,14,Frespond to all your calls.
OL,16,F"One notable road closure on Ralph
OL,17,FAllen Drive, near the garden centre,
OL,18,Fwhich requires 40m of resurfacing due
OL,19,Fto the tarmac lifting. We cannot give
OL,20,Fa timescale for this work currently."
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/5
