OL,3,CFlash flooding in Somerset after
OL,4,Ccounty hit by 18,540 lightning strikes
OL,6,FA red weather warning for extreme heat
OL,7,Fremains in place, stretching from
OL,8,FLondon to Swansea and Somerset to
OL,9,FBirmingham, from 9am on Wednesday to
OL,10,F9pm on Thursday.
